milar custom schemes used by the DHIS2 Android\napp (and any OAuth2 native-app per RFC 8252) were rejected. Editing any\nexisting client that had such a redirect URI failed with 409.\n\nReplace the UrlValidator check with java.net.URI parsing: accept anything\nwell-formed that has a scheme. Spring Authorization Server does the\nactual redirect-URI matching at authorize time, so we don't need to\ngate on URL shape at save time.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"aaf9419871b15a19a529b9f9021a34317b7d896c","tree_id":"39cf672eeab66a10dc169fddef1b4a76c0916798","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:27:01Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. 